Subject: Re: [T2] Weber Progressive setup Question

Sounds like the jets/emulsion tubes are not correctly sized for the flow of 
your motor. This is typical with the Weber carb. They sell them to fit a 
whole bunch of motors and most come jetted for 1500/1600cc. Find Pierce 
Manifolds for Weber jets and knowledge.

